{"tid":1960302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街仔Lewis Chung 呃錢 有前科","createTime":"2020-04-06T05:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-06T14:58:53.000Z","uid":50745,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ed03fc9fe302bda3070e4c7f572edc83bb3a3a12","tid":1960302,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:28:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivDQn4Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivDQn4Q.jpg&h=c20ebfc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事緣我個friend(肯定係我)係度買coin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3UpLWsN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3UpLWsN.jpg&h=c045e9f7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n俾左錢之後條友就深潛<br />\n仲delete埋個convo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後問番佢就已讀不回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3LVvoaX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3LVvoaX.jpg&h=8dd8b8d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t7BqWtu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft7BqWtu.jpg&h=2db457b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然用得FPS就有佢個電話<br />\n都有埋佢個樣啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aUu0Lnc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaUu0Lnc.jpg&h=8a09f95d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JANtUfz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJANtUfz.jpg&h=7c56ac79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今朝google起條友底<br />\n睇到條仆街仲要有前科</span><br />\n有條毒撚為左三千扮黃呃人 電話51778301<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1933707/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1933707/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當然佢個電話已經expire左無用<br />\n不過佢個撚屌樣仲係一樣<br />\nanyway<br />\n驚已報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條友有前科<br />\n你唔好諗住今次會好似上次個PO咁不了了之<br />\n推到佢仆街<br />\n廢事下次第個手足中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>係你呀鍾生</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivDQn4Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivDQn4Q.jpg&h=c20ebfc6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">名: Lewis Chung<br />\nChung Kx Cxxxx<br />\n可能名: <br />\nKx: Ka, Ki<br />\nCxxxx: Chuen, Ching, Cheng, Cheuk, Chong<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">歡迎大家一齊估佢個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a564da15c1225131feaf5108260aa2752c453e38","tid":1960302,"uid":50745,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:31:43.000Z","msg":"條仆街有前科<br />\n有條毒撚為左三千扮黃呃人 電話51778301<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1933707/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1933707/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ivDQn4Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FivDQn4Q.jpg&h=c20ebfc6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fbc0a7c04054b94dba65779e632a90b6124b339f","tid":1960302,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T05:32:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416b8c3b373918b797c38d30790a93a9d21c197b","tid":1960302,"uid":50745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20